{"id":"809332168249704449","type":"text","timestamp":1771839302,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/809332168249704449","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/foxgirlpirate/792705029242044416\">foxgirlpirate</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/summerash17/792687311947251712\">summerash17</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/foxgirlpirate/792560168856666112\">foxgirlpirate</a>:</p><blockquote><p>Everyone thinks that the Tumblr trans fem community is this giant conglomerate of a bunch of unknown people and faces when in reality it’s like, a few dozen of us, all following each other and posting silly and horny stuff. And most of us are burnt out, depressed, and broke and just looking to enjoy the small things in life like making each other smile. It’s pretty neat I think</p></blockquote><p>Reblog to make the tumblr trans fem community sillier, hornier, less burnt out, less depressed, less broke, and with more enjoyment with maximum Smileage</p></blockquote><p>Very important addition to this post^^</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"foxgirlpirate","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":1280,"header_full_height":771,"header_focus_width":1279,"header_focus_height":720,"avatar_shape":"square","background_color":"#91291A","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"40,1279,760,0","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/8952f402e5448a13f7c2ead0c1e60cf5/e8cb8dd9b5f60792-58/s1280x771/5450ec9cbf3bb5ec779542d3257e20d31df2d8e5.png","header_image_focused":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/8952f402e5448a13f7c2ead0c1e60cf5/e8cb8dd9b5f60792-58/s2048x3072_c0,5188,99922,98573/ebd2e10d0358357174a672439c42b15269a8ce42.png","header_image_poster":"","header_image_scaled":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/8952f402e5448a13f7c2ead0c1e60cf5/e8cb8dd9b5f60792